Package: MarketingAnalytics
Type: Package
Title: Marketing Analytics in R: Statistical Modeling
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Verena Pflieger
Maintainer: Verena Pflieger <verena.pflieger@inwt-statistics.de>
Description: The package bundels the functionalities needed for Marketing Analytics, in specific: 
    linear regression e.g. for customer lifetime modeling
    logistic regression e.g. for churn prevention
    survival analysis with time-invariant covariates e.g. for modeling time until churn
    principal component analysis for dimension reduction e.g. for extensice customer relation data
Depends: 
Imports: boot, car, corrplot, descr, ggplot2, Hmisc, MASS, muhaz, ROCR, rms, SDMTools, survival
Suggests: 
License: GNU General Public Version 3.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
